'''GFFA''' may refer to either:

*The [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances]], the successor state of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] which emerged during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].
*The "[[The galaxy|Galaxy Far, Far Away]]," a term among the ''[[Star Wars]]'' fandom that refers to the ''Star Wars'' galaxy as a whole.

